# ADLC Framework
# NOTE: ARCHITECTURE.md and gap-report.md are durable cross-team docs and are
# tracked (not ignored) — they were committed on the worktree branch and
# remain useful for future onboarding sessions.
# Per-item working files in .session/ are local-only; templates are committed.
.session/specs/*
!.session/specs/_templates/
!.session/specs/_templates/**
.session/learnings/*
!.session/learnings/.gitkeep
.env.monitor
